content: I'm also interested in learning more about the value of my vintage cameras. Can you recommend any resources or websites to help me determine the value of my rare 1960s rangefinder, and also give me an idea of how much I should expect to pay for similar cameras in the future? By the way, the comic book convention was amazing, and I got to meet the artist who signed my Spider-Man comics - I even got a sketch of Spider-Man on a variant cover.
